spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_INTR_DATA_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:displayName: C S AXI INTR DATA WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of S_AXI data bus

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_INTR_ADDR_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:displayName: C S AXI INTR ADDR WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of S_AXI address bus

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_NUM_OF_INTR
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Number of Interrupts

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_INTR_SENSITIVITY
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Each bit corresponds to Sensitivity of interrupt : 0 - EDGE, 1 - LEVEL

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_INTR_ACTIVE_STATE
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Each bit corresponds to Sub-type of INTR: [0 - FALLING_EDGE, 1 - RISING_EDGE : if C_INTR_SENSITIVITY is EDGE(0)] and [ 0 - LEVEL_LOW, 1 - LEVEL_LOW : if C_INTR_SENSITIVITY is LEVEL(1) ]

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_IRQ_SENSITIVITY
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Sensitivity of IRQ: 0 - EDGE, 1 - LEVEL

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_IRQ_ACTIVE_STATE
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Sub-type of IRQ: [0 - FALLING_EDGE, 1 - RISING_EDGE : if C_IRQ_SENSITIVITY is EDGE(0)] and [ 0 - LEVEL_LOW, 1 - LEVEL_LOW : if C_IRQ_SENSITIVITY is LEVEL(1) ]

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S00_AXI_DATA_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of S_AXI data bus

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S00_AXI_ADDR_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of S_AXI address bus

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M00_AXIS_TDATA_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of S_AXIS address bus. The slave accepts the read and write addresses of width C_M_AXIS_TDATA_WIDTH.

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M00_AXIS_START_COUNT
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Start count is the numeber of clock cycles the master will wait before initiating/issuing any transaction.

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M02_AXI_START_DATA_VALUE
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:displayName: C M02 AXI START DATA VALUE
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: The master will start generating data from the C_M_START_DATA_VALUE value

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M02_AXI_TARGET_SLAVE_BASE_ADDR
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:displayName: C M02 AXI TARGET SLAVE BASE ADDR
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: The master requires a target slave base address. // The master will initiate read and write transactions on the slave with base address specified here as a parameter.

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M02_AXI_ADDR_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of M_AXI address bus. // The master generates the read and write addresses of width specified as C_M_AXI_ADDR_WIDTH.

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M02_AXI_DATA_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of M_AXI data bus. // The master issues write data and accept read data where the width of the data bus is C_M_AXI_DATA_WIDTH

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M02_AXI_TRANSACTIONS_NUM
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Transaction number is the number of write // and read transactions the master will perform as a part of this example memory test.
